{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01J3FDs9nufaMYzx4G2T5SdG","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013osTaz3GBdDqm89ZTfrEr1","name":"mcp__flywheel__flywheel_commit_new_node","input":{"local_temp_node_id":"trees-workstream-branch","parent_ids":["646664d3-7ba6-5f80-952a-02d95baa722d"],"staged_payload":{"title":"Cluster: Trees — Workstream Plan & Feature Engineering (WC2026)","content":"## Workstream: Tree Ensembles for WC2026 Match Prediction\n\n### Hypothesis\nTree ensembles (RandomForest, ExtraTrees, HistGradientBoosting) can leverage the full engineered pre-match feature set — Elo/rank diffs, squad strength aggregates, confederation, host flag, venue capacity/elevation — to beat the Elo-logistic baseline. Heavy regularisation is required given only 64 samples.\n\n### Feature Engineering Plan\nPre-match features used (no leakage):\n- **Elo/rank**: `elo_diff`, `rank_diff`, absolute `home_elo_rating`, `away_elo_rating`, `home_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`, `away_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`\n- **Squad aggregates** (all pre-tournament): `squad_total_mv`, `squad_top11_mv`, `squad_mean_caps`, `squad_total_goals`, `squad_mean_age`, `squad_mean_height`, `gk_mv`, `att_goals` — both home/away and diff forms\n- **Context**: `home_is_host` / `away_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN), `stage_enc` (0–4), `capacity`, `elevation_meters`\n- **Categorical**: `home_confederation`, `away_confederation` (OrdinalEncoded inside CV)\n\nTotal: 34 features across 64 samples → heavy regularisation required.\n\n### Regularisation Strategy\n- RandomForest/ExtraTrees: `max_depth=3–5`, `min_samples_leaf=4–8`, `n_estimators=100–200`, `max_features=0.5`\n- HGB: `max_depth=2–3`, `min_samples_leaf=10–20`, `l2_regularization=1.0–10.0`, `n_iter_no_change=5`\n- All with `random_state=0`; monotonic constraints where sensible (Elo diff → H probability positive)\n\n### Experiment Branches\n1. **Elo-only logistic** — reference baseline (measured here, not just stated)\n2. **RF-v1** — RandomForest heavily regularised (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 100 trees)\n3. **ET-v1** — ExtraTrees (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 200 trees)\n4. **HGB-v1** — HistGradientBoosting (depth=3, min_leaf=20, l2=5.0)\n5. **RF-Elo-only** — RF with only Elo/rank features (ablation)\n6. **HGB-tuned** — best HGB hyperparameters from grid\n\nCV protocol: RepeatedStratifiedKFold(5 folds × 10 repeats, seed 0). Encoders fit inside folds only.\n\n### Validity\n- No post-match features used\n- All encoders/scalers fit inside CV folds\n- Seed 0 throughout\n- CPU-only (4 vCPU box)\n","summary":"Trees workstream plan: run RandomForest, ExtraTrees, and HistGradientBoosting on 34 pre-match features (Elo/rank diffs + squad aggregates + host flag + venue) across 64 samples. Heavy regularisation (max_depth ≤ 5, min_samples_leaf ≥ 4) required. Branches into 5+ experiment nodes; target: beat Elo-logistic CV log-loss.","repo_context":{"repo_url":null,"branch_name":null,"head_commit_sha":null,"origin_host":null,"updated_by":null,"external_transcript_ref":null}}},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5082,"cache_read_input_tokens":50310,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5082},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"280583a0-a049-4eb6-83aa-7a9742105563","uuid":"930840a8-1f83-4e67-b72f-5955cf167b3d","request_id":"req_011CcVNqDFJMrkbyNzLkfSqC"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013osTaz3GBdDqm89ZTfrEr1","type":"tool_result","content":"{\"local_temp_node_id\":\"trees-workstream-branch\",\"node\":{\"node_id\":\"08e8a83a-ae0c-5053-9502-43e601976e90\",\"slug_name\":\"dawn-sea-7100\",\"parent_ids\":[\"646664d3-7ba6-5f80-952a-02d95baa722d\"],\"child_ids\":[],\"title\":\"Cluster: Trees — Workstream Plan & Feature Engineering (WC2026)\",\"content\":\"## Workstream: Tree Ensembles for WC2026 Match Prediction\\n\\n### Hypothesis\\nTree ensembles (RandomForest, ExtraTrees, HistGradientBoosting) can leverage the full engineered pre-match feature set — Elo/rank diffs, squad strength aggregates, confederation, host flag, venue capacity/elevation — to beat the Elo-logistic baseline. Heavy regularisation is required given only 64 samples.\\n\\n### Feature Engineering Plan\\nPre-match features used (no leakage):\\n- **Elo/rank**: `elo_diff`, `rank_diff`, absolute `home_elo_rating`, `away_elo_rating`, `home_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`, `away_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`\\n- **Squad aggregates** (all pre-tournament): `squad_total_mv`, `squad_top11_mv`, `squad_mean_caps`, `squad_total_goals`, `squad_mean_age`, `squad_mean_height`, `gk_mv`, `att_goals` — both home/away and diff forms\\n- **Context**: `home_is_host` / `away_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN), `stage_enc` (0–4), `capacity`, `elevation_meters`\\n- **Categorical**: `home_confederation`, `away_confederation` (OrdinalEncoded inside CV)\\n\\nTotal: 34 features across 64 samples → heavy regularisation required.\\n\\n### Regularisation Strategy\\n- RandomForest/ExtraTrees: `max_depth=3–5`, `min_samples_leaf=4–8`, `n_estimators=100–200`, `max_features=0.5`\\n- HGB: `max_depth=2–3`, `min_samples_leaf=10–20`, `l2_regularization=1.0–10.0`, `n_iter_no_change=5`\\n- All with `random_state=0`; monotonic constraints where sensible (Elo diff → H probability positive)\\n\\n### Experiment Branches\\n1. **Elo-only logistic** — reference baseline (measured here, not just stated)\\n2. **RF-v1** — RandomForest heavily regularised (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 100 trees)\\n3. **ET-v1** — ExtraTrees (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 200 trees)\\n4. **HGB-v1** — HistGradientBoosting (depth=3, min_leaf=20, l2=5.0)\\n5. **RF-Elo-only** — RF with only Elo/rank features (ablation)\\n6. **HGB-tuned** — best HGB hyperparameters from grid\\n\\nCV protocol: RepeatedStratifiedKFold(5 folds × 10 repeats, seed 0). Encoders fit inside folds only.\\n\\n### Validity\\n- No post-match features used\\n- All encoders/scalers fit inside CV folds\\n- Seed 0 throughout\\n- CPU-only (4 vCPU box)\\n\",\"origin_host\":null,\"updated_by\":null,\"external_transcript_ref\":null,\"revision\":0,\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:55:22.966026+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:55:22.966026+00:00\",\"graph_tags\":[],\"tag_ids\":[],\"tag_history\":[],\"graph_projection\":\"full\",\"summary\":\"Trees workstream plan: run RandomForest, ExtraTrees, and HistGradientBoosting on 34 pre-match features (Elo/rank diffs + squad aggregates + host flag + venue) across 64 samples. Heavy regularisation (max_depth ≤ 5, min_samples_leaf ≥ 4) required. Branches into 5+ experiment nodes; target: beat Elo-logistic CV log-loss.\",\"artifacts\":[],\"executions\":[]},\"committed_revision\":0,\"staged_changes_pending\":false,\"commit_required\":false,\"next_action_hint\":\"commit complete; no staged changes pending\"}"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"280583a0-a049-4eb6-83aa-7a9742105563","uuid":"f4dc790c-5668-49fd-982d-02c94f5a3c90","timestamp":"2026-06-28T08:55:23.086Z","tool_use_result":{"content":"{\"local_temp_node_id\":\"trees-workstream-branch\",\"node\":{\"node_id\":\"08e8a83a-ae0c-5053-9502-43e601976e90\",\"slug_name\":\"dawn-sea-7100\",\"parent_ids\":[\"646664d3-7ba6-5f80-952a-02d95baa722d\"],\"child_ids\":[],\"title\":\"Cluster: Trees — Workstream Plan & Feature Engineering (WC2026)\",\"content\":\"## Workstream: Tree Ensembles for WC2026 Match Prediction\\n\\n### Hypothesis\\nTree ensembles (RandomForest, ExtraTrees, HistGradientBoosting) can leverage the full engineered pre-match feature set — Elo/rank diffs, squad strength aggregates, confederation, host flag, venue capacity/elevation — to beat the Elo-logistic baseline. Heavy regularisation is required given only 64 samples.\\n\\n### Feature Engineering Plan\\nPre-match features used (no leakage):\\n- **Elo/rank**: `elo_diff`, `rank_diff`, absolute `home_elo_rating`, `away_elo_rating`, `home_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`, `away_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`\\n- **Squad aggregates** (all pre-tournament): `squad_total_mv`, `squad_top11_mv`, `squad_mean_caps`, `squad_total_goals`, `squad_mean_age`, `squad_mean_height`, `gk_mv`, `att_goals` — both home/away and diff forms\\n- **Context**: `home_is_host` / `away_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN), `stage_enc` (0–4), `capacity`, `elevation_meters`\\n- **Categorical**: `home_confederation`, `away_confederation` (OrdinalEncoded inside CV)\\n\\nTotal: 34 features across 64 samples → heavy regularisation required.\\n\\n### Regularisation Strategy\\n- RandomForest/ExtraTrees: `max_depth=3–5`, `min_samples_leaf=4–8`, `n_estimators=100–200`, `max_features=0.5`\\n- HGB: `max_depth=2–3`, `min_samples_leaf=10–20`, `l2_regularization=1.0–10.0`, `n_iter_no_change=5`\\n- All with `random_state=0`; monotonic constraints where sensible (Elo diff → H probability positive)\\n\\n### Experiment Branches\\n1. **Elo-only logistic** — reference baseline (measured here, not just stated)\\n2. **RF-v1** — RandomForest heavily regularised (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 100 trees)\\n3. **ET-v1** — ExtraTrees (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 200 trees)\\n4. **HGB-v1** — HistGradientBoosting (depth=3, min_leaf=20, l2=5.0)\\n5. **RF-Elo-only** — RF with only Elo/rank features (ablation)\\n6. **HGB-tuned** — best HGB hyperparameters from grid\\n\\nCV protocol: RepeatedStratifiedKFold(5 folds × 10 repeats, seed 0). Encoders fit inside folds only.\\n\\n### Validity\\n- No post-match features used\\n- All encoders/scalers fit inside CV folds\\n- Seed 0 throughout\\n- CPU-only (4 vCPU box)\\n\",\"origin_host\":null,\"updated_by\":null,\"external_transcript_ref\":null,\"revision\":0,\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:55:22.966026+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:55:22.966026+00:00\",\"graph_tags\":[],\"tag_ids\":[],\"tag_history\":[],\"graph_projection\":\"full\",\"summary\":\"Trees workstream plan: run RandomForest, ExtraTrees, and HistGradientBoosting on 34 pre-match features (Elo/rank diffs + squad aggregates + host flag + venue) across 64 samples. Heavy regularisation (max_depth ≤ 5, min_samples_leaf ≥ 4) required. Branches into 5+ experiment nodes; target: beat Elo-logistic CV log-loss.\",\"artifacts\":[],\"executions\":[]},\"committed_revision\":0,\"staged_changes_pending\":false,\"commit_required\":false,\"next_action_hint\":\"commit complete; no staged changes pending\"}","structuredContent":{"local_temp_node_id":"trees-workstream-branch","node":{"node_id":"08e8a83a-ae0c-5053-9502-43e601976e90","slug_name":"dawn-sea-7100","parent_ids":["646664d3-7ba6-5f80-952a-02d95baa722d"],"child_ids":[],"title":"Cluster: Trees — Workstream Plan & Feature Engineering (WC2026)","content":"## Workstream: Tree Ensembles for WC2026 Match Prediction\n\n### Hypothesis\nTree ensembles (RandomForest, ExtraTrees, HistGradientBoosting) can leverage the full engineered pre-match feature set — Elo/rank diffs, squad strength aggregates, confederation, host flag, venue capacity/elevation — to beat the Elo-logistic baseline. Heavy regularisation is required given only 64 samples.\n\n### Feature Engineering Plan\nPre-match features used (no leakage):\n- **Elo/rank**: `elo_diff`, `rank_diff`, absolute `home_elo_rating`, `away_elo_rating`, `home_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`, `away_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`\n- **Squad aggregates** (all pre-tournament): `squad_total_mv`, `squad_top11_mv`, `squad_mean_caps`, `squad_total_goals`, `squad_mean_age`, `squad_mean_height`, `gk_mv`, `att_goals` — both home/away and diff forms\n- **Context**: `home_is_host` / `away_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN), `stage_enc` (0–4), `capacity`, `elevation_meters`\n- **Categorical**: `home_confederation`, `away_confederation` (OrdinalEncoded inside CV)\n\nTotal: 34 features across 64 samples → heavy regularisation required.\n\n### Regularisation Strategy\n- RandomForest/ExtraTrees: `max_depth=3–5`, `min_samples_leaf=4–8`, `n_estimators=100–200`, `max_features=0.5`\n- HGB: `max_depth=2–3`, `min_samples_leaf=10–20`, `l2_regularization=1.0–10.0`, `n_iter_no_change=5`\n- All with `random_state=0`; monotonic constraints where sensible (Elo diff → H probability positive)\n\n### Experiment Branches\n1. **Elo-only logistic** — reference baseline (measured here, not just stated)\n2. **RF-v1** — RandomForest heavily regularised (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 100 trees)\n3. **ET-v1** — ExtraTrees (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 200 trees)\n4. **HGB-v1** — HistGradientBoosting (depth=3, min_leaf=20, l2=5.0)\n5. **RF-Elo-only** — RF with only Elo/rank features (ablation)\n6. **HGB-tuned** — best HGB hyperparameters from grid\n\nCV protocol: RepeatedStratifiedKFold(5 folds × 10 repeats, seed 0). Encoders fit inside folds only.\n\n### Validity\n- No post-match features used\n- All encoders/scalers fit inside CV folds\n- Seed 0 throughout\n- CPU-only (4 vCPU box)\n","origin_host":null,"updated_by":null,"external_transcript_ref":null,"revision":0,"created_at":"2026-06-28T08:55:22.966026+00:00","updated_at":"2026-06-28T08:55:22.966026+00:00","graph_tags":[],"tag_ids":[],"tag_history":[],"graph_projection":"full","summary":"Trees workstream plan: run RandomForest, ExtraTrees, and HistGradientBoosting on 34 pre-match features (Elo/rank diffs + squad aggregates + host flag + venue) across 64 samples. Heavy regularisation (max_depth ≤ 5, min_samples_leaf ≥ 4) required. Branches into 5+ experiment nodes; target: beat Elo-logistic CV log-loss.","artifacts":[],"executions":[]},"committed_revision":0,"staged_changes_pending":false,"commit_required":false,"next_action_hint":"commit complete; no staged changes pending"}}}
