28T08:56:19.765109+00:00","content":"## Workstream: Tree Ensembles for WC2026 Match Prediction\n\n### Hypothesis\nTree ensembles (RandomForest, ExtraTrees, HistGradientBoosting) can leverage the full engineered pre-match feature set — Elo/rank diffs, squad strength aggregates, confederation, host flag, venue capacity/elevation — to beat the Elo-logistic baseline. Heavy regularisation is required given only 64 samples.\n\n### Feature Engineering Plan\nPre-match features used (no leakage):\n- **Elo/rank**: `elo_diff`, `rank_diff`, absolute `home_elo_rating`, `away_elo_rating`, `home_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`, `away_fifa_ranking_pre_tournament`\n- **Squad aggregates** (all pre-tournament): `squad_total_mv`, `squad_top11_mv`, `squad_mean_caps`, `squad_total_goals`, `squad_mean_age`, `squad_mean_height`, `gk_mv`, `att_goals` — both home/away and diff forms\n- **Context**: `home_is_host` / `away_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN), `stage_enc` (0–4), `capacity`, `elevation_meters`\n- **Categorical**: `home_confederation`, `away_confederation` (OrdinalEncoded inside CV)\n\nTotal: 34 features across 64 samples → heavy regularisation required.\n\n### Regularisation Strategy\n- RandomForest/ExtraTrees: `max_depth=3–5`, `min_samples_leaf=4–8`, `n_estimators=100–200`, `max_features=0.5`\n- HGB: `max_depth=2–3`, `min_samples_leaf=10–20`, `l2_regularization=1.0–10.0`, `n_iter_no_change=5`\n- All with `random_state=0`; monotonic constraints where sensible (Elo diff → H probability positive)\n\n### Experiment Branches\n1. **Elo-only logistic** — reference baseline (measured here, not just stated)\n2. **RF-v1** — RandomForest heavily regularised (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 100 trees)\n3. **ET-v1** — ExtraTrees (depth=3, min_leaf=8, 200 trees)\n4. **HGB-v1** — HistGradientBoosting (depth=3, min_leaf=20, l2=5.0)\n5. **RF-Elo-only** — RF with only Elo/rank features (ablation)\n6. **HGB-tuned** — best HGB hyperparameters from grid\n\nCV protocol: RepeatedStratifiedKFold(5 folds × 10 repeats, seed 0). Encoders fit inside folds only.\n\n### Validity\n- No post-match features used\n- All encoders/scalers fit inside CV folds\n- Seed 0 throughout\n- CPU-only (4 vCPU box)\n","summary":"Trees workstream plan: run RandomForest, ExtraTrees, and HistGradientBoosting on 34 pre-match features (Elo/rank diffs + squad aggregates + host flag + venue) across 64 samples. Heavy regularisation (max_depth ≤ 5, min_samples_leaf ≥ 4) required. Branches into 5+ experiment nodes; target: beat Elo-logistic CV log-loss.","graph_tags":[{"tag_id":"tag-310643c63f5e","name":"Cluster: Trees","bg_color":"#2D6A4F","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-193b65acde49","name":"Cluster: Squad-Strength","bg_color":"#2563EB","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-a31dd0232ac0","name":"outcome:GREEN","bg_color":"#22C55E","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-c2b8915efd2c","name":"outcome:RED","bg_color":"#EF4444","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-68a8c67891ff","name":"outcome:NO-GO","bg_color":"#6B7280","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-30d0d746413f","name":"kind:experiment","bg_color":"#7C3AED","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-d074e5692a54","name":"setting:wc2026","bg_color":"#F59E0B","text_color":"#1F2937","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-f0aefdc501fb","name":"kind:experiment","bg_color":"#7C3AED","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false},{"tag_id":"tag-7f454d8c9542","name":"Cluster: Elo-Prior","bg_color":"#1A56DB","text_color":"#FFFFFF","one_only":false,"track_history":false}],"tag_ids":["tag-310643c63f5e"],"tag_history":[],"artifacts":[],"artifacts_total":0,"artifacts_truncated":false,"revision":2,"graph_projection":"full","is_owner":true,"visibility":"public","can_write":true,"can_admin":true,"owner_email":"k