{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01W8JXiFvvCqK4bxamjrCov8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01U3CXbBEY4xuaVDve7wHYhn","name":"mcp__flywheel__flywheel_commit_new_node","input":{"local_temp_node_id":"elo-baseline-node","parent_ids":["08e8a83a-ae0c-5053-9502-43e601976e90"],"staged_payload":{"title":"Baseline: Elo-logistic (elo_diff + home_is_host) — CV log-loss 0.8393 ± 0.274","content":"## Hypothesis\nLogistic regression on a single pre-match signal `elo_diff = home_elo - away_elo` plus `home_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN indicator) establishes the Elo-logistic reference baseline for the Trees workstream.\n\n## Setup / Config\n- **Features**: `elo_diff`, `home_is_host` (2 features)\n- **Model**: `LogisticRegression(C=1.0, max_iter=1000, random_state=0)`\n- **CV**: `RepeatedStratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, n_repeats=10, random_state=0)` = 50 folds\n- **Encoder**: ColumnTransformer (passthrough, no categoricals in this feature set) — fit inside CV\n- **Data**: 64 completed WC2026 matches; labels H/D/A (31/18/15)\n\n## Results\n| Metric | Mean | Std |\n|--------|------|-----|\n| **log-loss** | **0.8393** | **0.2746** |\n| accuracy | 0.6374 | 0.0814 |\n\n**Vs campaign baselines:**\n- Marginal prior (1.06): Δ −0.221 (GREEN — beats random)\n- Home-always (acc 48.4%): Δ +15.3 pp accuracy (GREEN)\n- This is the Elo-logistic reference the Trees cluster must beat\n\n## Interpretation\nElo difference alone is a strong signal: 63.7% accuracy and 0.84 log-loss vs 1.06 marginal prior. The std of 0.275 is high, reflecting genuine small-sample variance across 50 CV folds (64 rows, 5-fold → ~12 test rows per fold). Tree models must beat 0.8393 log-loss to show value.","summary":"Elo-logistic baseline: LogReg on elo_diff + home_is_host achieves CV log-loss 0.8393 ± 0.2746 and accuracy 63.74% (50 folds, seed 0). Beats marginal prior (1.06) by 0.221 log-loss units. This is the Trees workstream reference point; GREEN vs prior, sets target for tree models.","repo_context":{"repo_url":null,"branch_name":null,"head_commit_sha":null,"origin_host":null,"updated_by":null,"external_transcript_ref":null}}},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1027,"cache_read_input_tokens":67375,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1027},"output_tokens":40,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"280583a0-a049-4eb6-83aa-7a9742105563","uuid":"ee4c631e-a443-4f56-9b90-ce29eafba049","request_id":"req_011CcVNxbRjkrKg2dj9Hu65A"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01U3CXbBEY4xuaVDve7wHYhn","type":"tool_result","content":"{\"local_temp_node_id\":\"elo-baseline-node\",\"node\":{\"node_id\":\"6fff0d3a-0e96-5340-b84f-c4e41024dd3b\",\"slug_name\":\"empty-queen-7998\",\"parent_ids\":[\"08e8a83a-ae0c-5053-9502-43e601976e90\"],\"child_ids\":[],\"title\":\"Baseline: Elo-logistic (elo_diff + home_is_host) — CV log-loss 0.8393 ± 0.274\",\"content\":\"## Hypothesis\\nLogistic regression on a single pre-match signal `elo_diff = home_elo - away_elo` plus `home_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN indicator) establishes the Elo-logistic reference baseline for the Trees workstream.\\n\\n## Setup / Config\\n- **Features**: `elo_diff`, `home_is_host` (2 features)\\n- **Model**: `LogisticRegression(C=1.0, max_iter=1000, random_state=0)`\\n- **CV**: `RepeatedStratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, n_repeats=10, random_state=0)` = 50 folds\\n- **Encoder**: ColumnTransformer (passthrough, no categoricals in this feature set) — fit inside CV\\n- **Data**: 64 completed WC2026 matches; labels H/D/A (31/18/15)\\n\\n## Results\\n| Metric | Mean | Std |\\n|--------|------|-----|\\n| **log-loss** | **0.8393** | **0.2746** |\\n| accuracy | 0.6374 | 0.0814 |\\n\\n**Vs campaign baselines:**\\n- Marginal prior (1.06): Δ −0.221 (GREEN — beats random)\\n- Home-always (acc 48.4%): Δ +15.3 pp accuracy (GREEN)\\n- This is the Elo-logistic reference the Trees cluster must beat\\n\\n## Interpretation\\nElo difference alone is a strong signal: 63.7% accuracy and 0.84 log-loss vs 1.06 marginal prior. The std of 0.275 is high, reflecting genuine small-sample variance across 50 CV folds (64 rows, 5-fold → ~12 test rows per fold). Tree models must beat 0.8393 log-loss to show value.\",\"origin_host\":null,\"updated_by\":null,\"external_transcript_ref\":null,\"revision\":0,\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:56:56.903836+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:56:56.903836+00:00\",\"graph_tags\":[],\"tag_ids\":[],\"tag_history\":[]