{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ds5LY41sM3y7zJptE7fyDm","type":"tool_result","content":"{\"node\":{\"node_id\":\"6fff0d3a-0e96-5340-b84f-c4e41024dd3b\",\"slug_name\":\"empty-queen-7998\",\"parent_ids\":[\"08e8a83a-ae0c-5053-9502-43e601976e90\"],\"child_ids\":[],\"title\":\"Baseline: Elo-logistic (elo_diff + home_is_host) — CV log-loss 0.8393 ± 0.274\",\"content\":\"## Hypothesis\\nLogistic regression on a single pre-match signal `elo_diff = home_elo - away_elo` plus `home_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN indicator) establishes the Elo-logistic reference baseline for the Trees workstream.\\n\\n## Setup / Config\\n- **Features**: `elo_diff`, `home_is_host` (2 features)\\n- **Model**: `LogisticRegression(C=1.0, max_iter=1000, random_state=0)`\\n- **CV**: `RepeatedStratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, n_repeats=10, random_state=0)` = 50 folds\\n- **Encoder**: ColumnTransformer (passthrough, no categoricals in this feature set) — fit inside CV\\n- **Data**: 64 completed WC2026 matches; labels H/D/A (31/18/15)\\n\\n## Results\\n| Metric | Mean | Std |\\n|--------|------|-----|\\n| **log-loss** | **0.8393** | **0.2746** |\\n| accuracy | 0.6374 | 0.0814 |\\n\\n**Vs campaign baselines:**\\n- Marginal prior (1.06): Δ −0.221 (GREEN — beats random)\\n- Home-always (acc 48.4%): Δ +15.3 pp accuracy (GREEN)\\n- This is the Elo-logistic reference the Trees cluster must beat\\n\\n## Interpretation\\nElo difference alone is a strong signal: 63.7% accuracy and 0.84 log-loss vs 1.06 marginal prior. The std of 0.275 is high, reflecting genuine small-sample variance across 50 CV folds (64 rows, 5-fold → ~12 test rows per fold). Tree models must beat 0.8393 log-loss to show value.\",\"origin_host\":null,\"updated_by\":null,\"external_transcript_ref\":null,\"revision\":1,\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:56:56.903836+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:57:59.038074+00:00\",\"graph_tags\":[],\"tag_ids\":[],\"tag_history\":[],\"graph_projection\":\"full\",\"summary\":\"Elo-logistic baseline: LogReg on elo_diff + home_is_host achieves CV log-loss 0.8393 ± 0.2746 and accuracy 63.74% (50 folds, seed 0). Beats marginal prior (1.06) by 0.221 log-loss units. This is the Trees workstream reference point; GREEN vs prior, sets target for tree models.\",\"artifacts\":[{\"note\":\"\",\"title\":\"CV Metrics — Elo-logistic baseline\",\"payload\":{\"path\":\"metrics.json\",\"media_type\":\"application/json\"},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:57:58.752582+00:00\",\"artifact_id\":\"98678903-060d-5e0a-bcbd-fd0bf16c908b\",\"execution_id\":null,\"storage_path\":\"artifacts/nodes/6fff0d3a-0e96-5340-b84f-c4e41024dd3b/98678903-060d-5e0a-bcbd-fd0bf16c908b.json\",\"artifact_type\":\"json\"},{\"note\":\"\",\"title\":\"Run config — Elo-logistic baseline\",\"payload\":{\"path\":\"run.json\",\"media_type\":\"application/json\"},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:57:59.037005+00:00\",\"artifact_id\":\"0cbc046a-67a5-5ab5-86dc-1a40091a7208\",\"execution_id\":null,\"storage_path\":\"artifacts/nodes/6fff0d3a-0e96-5340-b84f-c4e41024dd3b/0cbc046a-67a5-5ab5-86dc-1a40091a7208.json\",\"artifact_type\":\"json\"}],\"executions\":[]},\"artifacts\":[{\"artifact_id\":\"98678903-060d-5e0a-bcbd-fd0bf16c908b\",\"artifact_type\":\"json\",\"title\":\"CV Metrics — Elo-logistic baseline\",\"execution_id\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"note\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:57:58.752582+00:00\",\"storage_path\":\"artifacts/nodes/6fff0d3a-0e96-5340-b84f-c4e41024dd3b/98678903-060d-5e0a-bcbd-fd0bf16c908b.json\",\"payload\":{\"path\":\"metrics.json\",\"media_type\":\"application/json\"}},{\"artifact_id\":\"0cbc046a-67a5-5ab5-86dc-1a40091a7208\",\"artifact_type\":\"json\",\"title\":\"Run config — Elo-logistic baseline\",\"execution_id\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"note\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:57:59.037005+00:00\",\"storage_path\":\"artifacts/nodes/6fff0d3a-0e96-5340-b84f-c4e41024dd3b/0cbc046a-67a5-5ab5-86dc-1a40091a7208.json\",\"payload\":{\"path\":\"run.json\",\"media_type\":\"application/json\"}}]}"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"280583a0-a049-4eb6-83aa-7a9742105563","uuid":"58a50323-e91f-40ad-bb9f-425766919695","timestamp":"2026-06-28T08:57:59.270Z","tool_use_result":{"content":"{\"node\":{\"node_id\":\"6fff0d3a-0e96-5340-b84f-c4e41024dd3b\",\"slug_name\":\"empty-queen-7998\",\"parent_ids\":[\"08e8a83a-ae0c-5053-9502-43e601976e90\"],\"child_ids\":[],\"title\":\"Baseline: Elo-logistic (elo_diff + home_is_host) — CV log-loss 0.8393 ± 0.274\",\"content\":\"## Hypothesis\\nLogistic regression on a single pre-match signal `elo_diff = home_elo - away_elo` plus `home_is_host` (MEX/USA/CAN indicator) establishes the Elo-logistic reference baseline for the Trees workstream.\\n\\n## Setup / Config\\n- **Features**: `elo_diff`, `home_is_host` (2 features)\\n- **Model**: `LogisticRegression(C=1.0, max_iter=1000, random_state=0)`\\n- **CV**: `RepeatedStratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, n_repeats=10, random_state=0)` = 50 folds\\n- **Encoder**: ColumnTransformer (passthrough, no categoricals in this feature set) — fit inside CV\\n- **Data**: 64 completed WC2026 matches; labels H/D/A (31/18/15)\\n\\n## Results\\n| Metric | Mean | Std |\\n|--------|------|-----|\\n| **log-loss** | **0.8393** | **0.2746** |\\n| accuracy | 0.6374 | 0.0814 |\\n\\n**Vs campaign baselines:**\\n- Marginal prior (1.06): Δ −0.221 (GREEN — beats random)\\n- Home-always (acc 48.4%): Δ +15.3 pp accuracy (GREEN)\\n- This is the Elo-logistic reference the Trees cluster must beat\\n\\n## Interpretation\\nElo difference alone is a strong signal: 63.7% accuracy and 0.84 log-loss vs 1.06 marginal prior. The std of 0.275 is high, reflecting genuine small-sample variance across 50 CV folds (64 rows, 5-fold → ~12 test rows per fold). Tree models must beat 0.8393 log-loss to show value.\",\"origin_host\":null,\"updated_by\":null,\"external_transcript_ref\":null,\"revision\":1,\"created_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:56:56.903836+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-06-28T08:57: